1. Leng5 Chian3
Goa2 tak8-jit8 e5 ng3-bang7 kap ki5-to2 si7 “Chu2 ah, kek-khi2 hok8-heng” eng7 Sin5-ju2 choe3 bu2-khi3 lai5 heng-khi2 Su3-tou5 Heng5-toan7 teh hok8-heng. Ng3 bok8-phiau e5 chit tiam2 ku2-khi2 chong2-lek8-chian3, jiok8-the2 teh kam2-kak ia3-sian7, boe7 thang chiau3 sim sou2 ai3. Tui3 hit e5 ke3-lo5 soa3 thou3-huih, che si7 te7-gek8 e5 ap-pek, hit e5 cheng3-ku3 si7 chin ai3 ki5-to2, m7-ku2 sim-sin5 hou7 phaiN2 sin5 khah iaN5, boe7 oe7 ki5-to2, 2, 3 jit8 ku2 hou7 ki5-to2 e5 Sin5 pang3-sak, bo5 khui3-lat8, kap Siong7-te3 e5 kau-poe5 choat8-tng7 kui2-na7-jit8, chit e5 keng-giam7 si7 kui2-ni5 lai5 be7-bat u7 bo5 khui3-lat8 e5 sin3-giong2 seng-oah8, chit e5 si5-chun7 tui3 Beng5-ko2-ok hong-bin7 lai5 chhiaN2 khi3 thoan5-to7. SiuN7-lai5 siuN7-khi3 kiat-ko2, hou7 chhu3-lai7 hoaN7-chhiu2 ki5-to2, chi2-be7 e5 chhiu2 hoaN7 ti7 goa2 e5 hi3 teng2-bin7 e5 si5, phaiN2 sin5 e5 lat8 soa3 chiuN7 i e5 chhiu2 kam2-kak oe7 ba5, chong2-si7 chit si5 khi2 tui3 Siong7-te3 tit-tioh8 chu7-iu5, iau2-ku2 teh thou3-huih, kau-chian3 kek8-liat8, na7-si7 Chu2 e5 beng7-leng7 “Khia7 chai7 ti7 sin3 lai5 chian5-chin3.”
Na2 khoaN3 hiah e5 tui3 hi3 chhut e5 huih-kak, na2 pi-chong3 e5 koat-sim. “Chu2 ah! Goa2 beh sun7-than3” an2-ni ki5-to2 e5 si5, leng5 e5 bak8-chiu khoaN3-kiN3 tui3 thiN u7 eng-hoe e5 hoe-iap8 chit8-iap8 chit8-iap8 teh poe loh8-lai5, si7 teh ka3-si7 goa7-the2 “Jiok8-the2 e5 lang5” si7 khang-hi tit8-tit8 tah hiu2-noa7 khi3, che7 loh8 he2-chhia, tok8-tok8 choan sim pek-chhiat ki5-to2. ChiN2-siong7 hiaN-ti7 khoa3-sim lai5 KiaN-to chhia-cham7 sang3 goa2, na7-si7 bo5 oe7 thang kong2 ia7 be7 chhio3. Bi2-chhoan hiaN-ti7 choe3 chou7-chhiu2 saN-kap khi3, soan-kau3-su lai5 tan2-chih, ti7 iam7-jiat8 e5 tiong-kan khai-si2 thian-bou7 thoan5-to7. Chit si5 huih e5 chui2-choaN5 theng5-chi2, lai7-bin7 Sin5 e5 chui2-choaN5 khui, tit-tioh8 seng3-li7 e5 chu7-hoe7, tit-kiu3 e5 lang5, tit-tioh8 i-ho2 e5 lang5, siu7 Seng3 Sin5 chhiong-moa2 e5 lang5, choe7-choe7.
U7 chit8 cha2-khi2, thau3 cha2 ki5-to2 e5 si5, thiaN-kiN3 chhin-chhiuN7 io5-tang7 thiN hiah u7 lat8 Siong7-te3 e5 siaN “Li2 e5 ki5-to2 Goa2 i2-keng thiaN-kiN3.” Chhim-jip8 hi3-hu2, chhiong-moa2 leng5-lek8 kap khak-sin3. Lou7-be2 Chu2 chi2-si7 goa2, u7 chit8 e5 hiaN-ti7 ti7 ke3 si3-soaN3 e5 kau-chian3, goa2 na7 bo5 khi3 pang-chan7 i, oe7 sit-loh8 siN3-mia7. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 khi3 Pak-liok8 e5 Bu2-seng kau3-hoe7 mng7 “Ho5-tian5 hiaN-ti7 phoa3-piN7 si7 bo5?” Chong2-si7 i kong2 “Bo5! Iong2-iong2 teh pou3-to7.” Goa2 chiu7 khi3 thian-bou7 khoaN3-mai7, hiaN-ti7 jiat8 38-39 tou7 iau2-ku2 ke3-siok8 teh pou3-to7, loh8-hou7 e5 am3-si5 ia7 toa3 ti7 thian-bou7 chit kui2-jit8 bo5 chiah8 bo5 lim chin siau-san2, chek-si5 hou7 hiaN-ti7 tng2-khi3 kau3-hoe7 pou2-iong2.
Thian-bou7 pou3-to7 soah lah, hiaN-ti7 e5 siN3-mia7 tit-tioh8 kiu3, kau3-hoe7 tit-tioh8 chin toa7 e5 kiu3-un kap i-ti7 e5, hun3-heng-hoe7. Hit-am3 to2-loh8 bin5-chhng5, in-ui7 ke3-lo5, boe7 khun3-tit, chi2-u7 giong2-bong7 Chu2 lai5 ki5-to2, hit si5 goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 chang5 toa7 chang5 eng-hoe, kui chang5 khui kau3 chin sui2, bo5 ku2 thau3 chin toa7 hong-thai, eng-hoe io5 kau3 lian5 kun to beh puih8 khi2-lai5 e5 khoan2, hong-thai au7 eng-hoe long2 lak8 liau2-liau2, chi2-u7 ti7 e7-bin7 e5 iN2-a2 iau2 chhun 5 lui2, hit si5 Seng3 Sin5 e5 ka3-si7, “Goa2 kho3 jiok8-the2 e5 iong2, jiok8-the2 e5 ti3-hui7 teh thoan5-to7, in-ui7 te7-gek8 e5 koan5-lek8 teh chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-chang5 eng-hoe e5 pian3-chhian, tui3 chia khi2 tok8-tok8 tioh8 ti7 Seng3 Sin5 lai5 kiaN5.”
“Goan2 e5 goa7-the2 sui-jian5 pai7-hoai7, na7 si7 goan2 e5 lai7-sim jit8-jit8 oaN7-sin.” (II Ko-lim5-to 4:16)
2. Lim5-chai7 E5 He2
U7 chit8 pai2 siu7 chhiaN2 khi3 sun5-hoe5 San-im toe7-hng, he2-chhia chin-am3 tui3 KiaN-tou khui-chhia, thang kong2 si7 kut8-peng he2-chhia, chhia goa7 kui-phian3 si7 gun5 se3-kai3, pai7-chian3 boe7 loa7 ku2, hit si5 e5 jin5-sim to7-tek hu2-pai7, bo5 tiat8-su7, goa2 che7 hit-tiuN chhia, tu2-ho2 u7 KiaN-tou hu7-lu2-hoe7 e5 thoan5-the2 ia7 lai5 che7, tai7-ke long2 chheng7 chin-sui2, chiah e5 lang5 kau3 poaN3-mi5 chiu7 khai-si2 kong2 hit ho7 lang5 m7 kaN2 thiaN chhou-siok8 e5 oe7. Sun5-hoe5-tiong goa2 ti7 he2-chhia lai7 bo5 kong2-oe7 chin7 sim ki5-to2, ui7-tioh8 chu7-hoe7 pi7-pan7 sim, chong2-si7 hou7 chiah e5 lang5 ui5-lui5 teh, chhin-chhiuN7 ham7-loh8 te7-gek8 e5 tiong5-ui5, ki5-to2 e5 hou-khip ia7 siu7 chah8-tng7, siang-chhiu2 ng hi7-khang m7 ai3 thiaN lai5 ki5-to2 na7 si7 be7 ke3-siok8. Goa2 e5 hi7-khang m7-thiaN na7-si7 te7-gek8 e5 toa7-chui2 keng3-jian5 chhiong-jip8, lai5 phah la5-sam5 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5, hou7 i oan5-choan5 bo5 leng5-lek8. Tui3 lai7-bin7 chheng3-chhut toa7 e5 thou2-khui3, ka7-ge5 chhiat-chhi2 kap khou2-bun7.
“Leng5-khou2 ti7 goa2 e5 Siong7-te3 e5 chhu3 kou3-mng5, khah ho2 tiam3 ti7 phaiN2-lang5 e5 pou3-piN5.” (Si-phian 84:10)
Ti7 hit khoan2 iu2-hek8 e5 si5 siong5-siong5 li7-khui i2, khi3 chhia-mng5-piN chhu choa2 che7 teh ki5-to2, chong2-si7 in-ui7 koaN5 ia7 boe7 ke3-siok8 oan5-choan5 si7 sit-pai7 chia2! Ah! Na7 an2-ni bin5-a2-chai3 e5 pou3-to7 un2-tang3 sit-pai7. ThiN-kng he2-chhia lai5 kau3 chhut hun5 tia7-sia7 hiah e5 lang5 chiu7 loh8-chhia, chhim-chhim the2-giam7 pai3 ngou2-siong7 e5 lang5 bo5 oah8-mia7 e5 sin3-giong2 seng-oah8 e5 khang-hi, hit khoan2 pai3 ngou2-siong7 e5 Jit8-pun2 kok-bin5 chin-chiaN3 si7 oah8 e5 sin-si. Ti7 chit e5 lang5 khang e5 he2-chhia lai7-bin7 chit8-e7, soa3 kam2-hong koaN5 tioh8, ah! Chin chiaN3 si7 siu7 chiu3-chou2 e5 ngou2-siong7 he2-chhia!
Ti7 To2-kun koan7 e5 chit8 tiau5 ke-lou7 teh pou3-to7, chong2-si7 sau3 koh hoat-jiat8, chu7-mng7 chu7-tap; che ia7 si7 Sin5-ju2 thoan5-to7-chia2 mah? Sit8-chai7 khou2-chian3. Ti7 hia u7 hoan7 tioh8 sin5-keng thiaN3 e5 hiaN-ti7, 14 ni5 ku2 aN3 ti7 he2-lang5 e5 teng2-bin7 teh ke3-mi5, pi2 phoa3-siuN3 e5 lang5 khah khou2-chham2. Hou7 chin choe7 i-seng ti7-liau5 bo5 kong-hau7, chian3-si5 tiong bian2-kiong2 boe2 chhia-toaN khi3 Him5-pun2 chhe7 hoat-su hou7 i liam7-chiu3, chong2-si7 long2 bo5 hau7, tui3 Chu2 e5 un-hui7, chiah-nih kiong5 e5 piN7, tui3 hit si5 tit-tioh8 i-ho2, kau3 kin-a2-jit8 iau2-ku2 iong2-kiaN7. Chong2-si7 goa2 sun5-hoe5 chiah e5 thoan5-to7-toe7 e5 tiong-kan, liu5-heng5 kam2-mou7 (Influenga) ok-hoa3, i2-keng tong3 boe7 tiau5, chit8 si5 Chu2 tui3 goa2 kong2 “Tng2-khi3 Sin5-hou7” pho7 tioh8 jiat8-pong3-pong3 e5 thau5-khak, tam5 kap sau3 kau-ka e5 tiong-kan, ian5-lou7 ki5-to2 chiah tng2-lai5 kau3 hak8-iN7.
Chu7 an2-ni to2-chhng5, bo5 hun mi5-jit8 khai-si2 Sin5-ju2 e5 ki5-to2. 3 jit8 ku2 e5 ki5-to2 liau2-au7, hit e7-pou 5 tiam2 bang5-bang5 e5 tiong-kan, goa2 e5 sin siu7 ku2-khi2, kau3 koan5 e5 sin5-leng5-kai3, choan5-sin siu7 Siong7-te3 e5 lim5-chai7 pau-ui5, hut-jian5 oat8-tng2-sin, Siong7-te3 e5 seng3-he2 teh toh8, hit e5 he2-iam7 jia-kham3 goa2 e5 thau5-khak, goa2 chai che si7 kui2 chheng ni5-cheng5 chi2-si7 Mou5-se chhi3-phe3 e5 he2-iam7 (Chhut Ai-kip8-ki3 2:4), bo5 ku2 chiah chai u7 bu5-sou3 e5 thiN-sai3 ui5 goa2, in che5-siaN tang5-chhiuN3 chan3-bi2 e5 koa.
“Toan7 khui phaiN2 sin5 e5 so2-lian7,<BR>SiuN2-su3 chu7-iu5 hou7 lang5,<BR>Hi-lian5 e5 cheng siaN,<BR>Ti7 am3-mi5 hian2-liang7.”
Au7-lai5 goa2 cheng-sin5, piN7 siu7 i-ho2, keh-jit8 khi2 koh chiau3-siong5 e5 seng-oah8! siuN7 khi2-lai5 si7 kan-khou2 1 le2-pai3 ku2 e5 huih e5 poe, chong2-si7 choe3-au7 tui3 Chu2 e5 seng3-chhiu2 seng5-chiap chiah toa7 chiok-hok e5 seng3-poe, chhong3-cho7 e5 Chu2, eng2-oan2 siu7 chheng-chan3, eng5-kng kui hou7 Bek8-ki-se2-tek e5 Siong7-te3 A-men.
3. Lok8-hng5
“I siu7 toa3 kau3 lok8-hng5, thiaN-kiN3 boe7 tit thang kong2 e5 oe7, chiu7-si7 lang5 sou2 m7 thang kong2 e5.” (II Ko-lim5-to 12:4)
Po2-lo5 siu7 toa3 kau3 te7 3 chan3 thiN, thang kap thian-kai3 e5 lang5 kau-poe5, chiau3 Sat-hu-sun-tai7 sou2 kong2 su3-tou5 sin3-keng tiong “goa2 sin3 seng3-tou5 e5 siong-thong” si7 siuN2-su3 toe7-chiuN7 sin3-tou5 thang kap leng5-kai3 e5 seng3-tou5 siong-thong, chong2-si7 iau3-kin2 tioh8 pi7-pan7 sim, ti7 hit lang5 e5 sim thiN-kai3 i2-keng khui, sou2-i2 te7 it iau3-kin2 si7 jit8-jit8 ng3 ka-ki7 si2, sun7-than3 Ki-tok lai5 oah8. Chit8 cha2-khi2 goa2 khun3-chhiN2, ti7 Seng3 Sin5 kau-poe5 e5 tiong-kan, goa2 e5 leng5-hun5 bo5 ti7 chit se3-kan, si7 ti7 sin5 e5 se3-kan, si7 ti7 boe7 tit thang kong2 sin5-seng3 leng5 ui5-khi3 e5 tiong-kan, ti7 lok8-hng5. Chong-giam5 e5 chhiu7-na5, hou7 chhiN-chhui3 pou3-moa2, kam2-kak boe7 tit thang kong2 e5 sin5-seng3.
Chit si5 tui3 hit peng5 e5 chhiu7-na5 hong2-hut thiaN-kiN3 chiau2 e5 siaN, chhun-thiN lan2 ti7 soaN-piN sou2 thiaN chin sui2 eng-a2 e5 siaN, oe7-gu2 koh-iuN7, na7-si7 siang7 hit e5 tiau7 teh chhiuN3 “Li7-khui jiok8-the2 ti7 sin5 lai5 oah8.” Ti7 thian-kai3 tak8 hang7 chiau5-pi7, bo5 sou2 khiam3-kheh, toe7-chiuN7 e5 mih8 si7 hit e5 iaN2, che Seng3-keng e5 oe7 si7 chin, khoaN3-kiN3 ti7 hia teh chhe e5 hong si7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 hong, si7 un-loan2 e5 thiaN3, ia7 khoaN3-kiN3 hou7 thiaN3 e5 hong kham3 moa2 e5 chhau2-bak8 teh tio5-thiau3. Chhim-sin3 bo5-lun7 chhau2-bak8, kang-ho5 chioh8-thau5 it-chhe3 e5 mih8 long2 oah8-oah8 teh kong2 khi2 Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng, teh chan3-bi2 Chu2 o-lo2 Chu2.
Hia si7 Ki-tok sou2 kiu3-siok8 e5 seng3-tou5 kap thiN-sai3 e5 kok, Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 a2-si7 chiau3 chit8 e5 Sin5-hak8-chia2 sou2 sia2 khak-sit8 lang5 siu7 cho7 si7 beh choe3 thiN-teng2 e5 kok-bin5, chiau3 sin5-hak8 e5 ka3-si7 thiaN-kai3 e5 thai3-iong5 chheng choe3 gi7 e5 thai3-iong5, chiu7 si7 Ki-tok pun2-sin, goa2 ia7 kui2-na7 pai2 khoaN3-kiN3 gi7 e5 thai3-iong5, koh hia e5 chhiN si7 seng3, oe7 hoat-chhut chin-li2 e5 kng. (Tan7-i2-li2 12:3) Chiau3 Seng3-keng sou2 ki3 ti7 toe7-chiuN7 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 kan-khou2 kau3 chaiN2-iuN7? Chiu7-si7 gia5 sip8-ji7-ke3 sun5 le2-chia2 e5 lou7-theng5, tioh8 eng7 ki5-to2 kau-chian3 kau3 thiat-te2. (Lou7-ka 16:23-30)
4. Te7-gek8
Goa2 chit8 pai2 tui3 siu-im-ki thiaN ke3 Gi7-keng (源義經) e5 seng-gai5. Jit8-pun2 choe7-choe7 lang5 tong5-cheng5 chit e5 lang5, chheng-chan3 i e5 choe3 lang5, chong2-si7 i pi-un7 e5 seng-gai5 si7 chaiN2-iuN7 u7 thang giau5-gi5, goa2 ia7 teh siuN7 chit tiam2, u7 chit8 am3 poaN3-mi5 khun3-chhiN2, u7 chit8 e5 si5-kan cheng7-cheng7 kap Siong7-te3 kau-poe5, chit si5 hut-jian5 tui3 thiN khi2 toa7 chhu2-be2-hong chhin-chhiuN7 kho2-phaN3 e5 hong-thai, hit e5 ui-lek8 si7 lian5 hak8-iN7 tiaN5-nih8 e5 chhiu7 kun to beh puih8 khi2-lai5, he si7 tui3 phaiN2 sin5 lai5 e5 toa7 hong, ti7 hit e5 au7-bin7 u7 thang kiaN e5 leng5 un-lun-khun5 ti7 goa2 e5 bin7-cheng5. Chit be2 lau7 choa5 khia5 tai7-seng e5 chhu2-be2-hong tui3 leng5-kai3 loh8 lai5, si7 beh tui3 te7-gek8 e5 ap-lek8 lai5 khou2-chhou2 goa2. Sin-khu kam2-kak kiaN-hiaN5, chi2-u7 ki5-kiu5 Chu2 e5 chin2-kiu3.
Bo5 ku2 goa2 siu7 hiat-loh8 te7-gek8, khia7 ti7 thang kiaN gia5 mng5-kng2 te7-gek8 e5 chit8 sou2-chai7, chit8 si5 thiaN-kiN3 u7 lang5 khou2-thang3 thou2-khui3 e5 siaN, kang7 si5-chun7 thiaN-kiN3 u7 siaN kong2 “Chia si7 te7-gek8 e5 Liam5-chhong lou7 (鎌倉通)”, goa2 chiu7 thau khoaN3 hit lai7-bin7, tioh8 chit8-kiaN si7 chit8 e5 siau3-lian5 eng-hiong5 to2 ti7 hia teh noa3. Choan5-sin hou7 tang5-lian7 khun2-pak8, chit lang5 chiu7-si7 Gi7-keng. I e5 chhui3 moa2-moa2 chiu3-chou2, i po3-siu5 e5 sim he2 toa7 toh8, toa7-siaN hoah beh chhut-khi3 tau5 Nai5-tiau5 (源賴朝), ke3-thau5 khou2 tou3 phah-phun2 sou2-i2 tang5 soaN3 sng3-jip8 choan5-sin, kut chih8 beh lih8 thang3 sim-koaN, choan5-sin huih sai-sai na2 ti7 chian3-tiuN5 sin-khu chin chhoah, siuN7 kong2 te7-chiuN7 kiam2 iau2 u7 chit khoan2 tou3-hun5 e5 bu2-su7.
Tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7 pak8 kah boe7 tin2-tang7 lai5 siu7 heng5-hoat8, chhin-chhiuN7 chit e5 chong7-thai7 i2-keng 700 goa7 ni5. Goa2 kha chun3 sin-khu gi7-gi7 chhoah boe7 tin2-tang7, chong2-si7 tit8-tit8 ki5-to2 Chu2 chiah thoat-chhut te7-gek8, mi5-si5 2 tiam2-cheng peh khi2-lai5 tiam2 100 chek e5 tian7-teng che7-teh, kiaN-hiaN5 koh kou-tok8 sin-khu leng5-hun5 gih8-gih8 chun3, bo5-lun7 ka-ku7, thian-pong5, po-le5 teng2 bak8-chiu sou2 khoaN3 long2 khoaN3 choe3 te7-gek8, si7 hou7 khiong2-pou3 kam2 sou2 ap-to2, chia khi2 1 le2-pai3 ku2, phe5-hu tui3 koan-chiat thiaN3 kau3 thau5-khak-be2, kam2-kak te7-gek8 e5 thang3-thiaN3 e5 ap-pek-kam2, 2 tiam2-cheng ku2 e5 te7-gek8 seng-oah8 to tong3 boe7 tiau5, chiu7 hiah e5 tioh8 eng2-oan2 toa3 ti7 chia e5 choe7-jin5 e5 un7-mia7 beh chaiN2-iuN7? Bo5 Ki-tok bo5 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 huih, bu2-su7-to7 si5-tai7 Jit8-pun2 lang5 e5 biat8-bo5 e5 cheng5-heng5 sit8-chai7 kho2-siong. Bo5-lun7 chaiN2-iuN7 e5 hi-seng, na7 bo5 soan-thoan5 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 hok-im, jin5-lui7 it-teng7 si7 biat8-bo5. Peng5-iu2 ah! Ui7-tioh8 chit hang7 lai5 chin7 li2 e5 choan5-lek8. A-men.
5. Ti7 Te7-gek8
Goa2 beh koh sia2 goa2 ti7 kim3-chiah8 ki5-to2 tiong siu7 chi2-si7 te7-gek8 e5 cheng5-heng5, goa2 in-ui7 ia3-sian7 tui3 e7-pou, chiu7 ti7 bin5-chhng5 teh ki5-to2. Chha-put-to keng-ke3 3 tiam2-cheng, chiu7 thiaN-kiN3 thang-kiaN e5 kha-pou7-siaN, hut-jian5 bak8-chiu thi2-khui khoaN3-kiN3 goa2 e5 bin5-chhng5-teng2 u7 toa7 chiah ou-bak8-bak8 e5 ou-hun5 ta3-oa2-lai5, chit8-si5-a2 chiu7 tit8-kam2 si7 te7-gek8 e5 phaiN2-sin5, tui3 phaiN2-sin5 lau5-chhut chit8-chiong2 e5 mou5-lek8 liah8-tiau5 goa2 e5 ngou2-the2, am7-kun2 hou7 so2-a2 pak8 kui2-na7-lin3, siu7 tioh8 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 beh ka7 goa2 chhui-si2 e5 ap-lek8, siuN7 beh ki5-to2, m7-na7 boe7 chhut-siaN, lian5 chih8-be2 ia7 ba5 kau3 boe7 tin2-tang7.
Choan5-sin put-si5 lian5 chng2-thau5-a2 to boe7 tin2-tang7, tui3 an2-ni goa2 hou7 phaiN2-sin5 hiat loh8 te7-gek8. Hia si7 chhin-chhiuN7 hong-hoe3 e5 Sou3-to-ma2 Gou5-mou5-lah8, ian-bu7 tui3 hia chheng3-khi2 kham3-bat8 te7-kiu5, lai5 koan2-hat lang5, suh tioh8 e5 lang5 long2 siu7 tiong3-hong (tng7 nau2-kun) hi3-lo5 khou2-chhou2, koh siu7-tioh8 i e5 kam2-hoa3 e5 lang5 long2 chiaN5 choe3 oan3-hun7, saN-chiN, thai5-lang5, choe7 e5 lou5-chai5. Beh tui3 Siong7-te3 ki5-to2 kiu5-kiu3, na7-si7 in-ui7 ke-thau5 e5 khun3-khou2 oan5-choan5 boe7 chhut siaN, lim2-lim2-a2 piaN3 chin7 lin-bo2-lat8 hoah “Chu2 Ia5-sou” chit 3 ji7 5 hun-cheng ku2 chiah hoah chhut-lai5 chin kan-khou2 e5 hoah-siaN. Kang7-si5-chun7 chhu3-piN e5 kau2-le5, jiau2-tong7 am3-mi5 e5 cheng7-siok8. Chit si5 Chu2 Ia5-sou ka7 goa2 thau2-pang3, khoaN3 si5-cheng tu2 11 tiam2, siu-iong2-seng chit8 e5 chi2-be7 kong2 i kiaN kau3 gia5 mng5-kng2, te7-gek8 e5 loe7-liu5 lau5-chhut toe7-chiuN7 lai5 khou2-chhou2 lang5, beh eng7 choe7, piN7 kap sia5-kau3 lai5 biat8-bo5 jin5-lui7, Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2 ah! Tioh8 kiu5 Kiu3 Chu2 Ia5-sou, tioh8 thoan5 Chu2 Ia5-sou oah8-mia7 e5 hok-im hou7 se3-kan lang5. A-men.
8. U7-gian5 E5 Sin5
U7 chit8 pai2 goa2 ti7 ki5-to2 e5 tiong-kan khoaN3-kiN3 thiN e5 chit8 kak khui, Siong7-te3 e5 eng5-kng tui3 hun5 e5 tiong-kan sia7-chhut, ti7 hit e5 kng e5 tiong-kan chhin-chhiuN7 he2 toh8 e5 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 chin7 chhut.
“Koh li2 thiaN-kiN3 I e5 oe7 tui3 he2-tiong chhut.” (Sin-beng7-ki3 4:36)
I e5 oe7 si7 ki3 ti7 Lo5-ma2 12:12 “Ti7 ng3-bang7 tioh8 hoaN-hi2, ti7 hoan7-lan7 tioh8 thun-lun2, ti7 ki5-to2, tioh8 siong5-siong5 Seng3-tou5 sou2 khiam3-kheh e5 chiu7 kiong-kip i.” Tng-si5 ui7-tioh8 saN-chiap soa3 leng5-hun5 jiok8-the2 kek8-liat8 e5 cheng-chian3, jiok8-the2 kau3-kek8 soe-jiok8 chhiN-ng5 pin5-hiat e5 chong7-thai7, khoaN3-tioh8 goa2 e5 lang5, long2 khng3 goa2 “An2-ni si7 bo5 hap8 ti7 soan-thoan5 i-ti7 e5 Siong7-te3 e5 thoan5-to7-chia2, tioh8 hoe5-hok8 kian7-khong.” Sou2-i2 goa2 ia7 siu7-tioh8 lai5 su-hiat hoe5-hok8 kian7-khong e5 iu2-hek8, chit si5 hou7 goa2 chit e5 oe7, chi2-si7 goa2 sou2 tioh8 kiaN5 e5 lou7, goa2 chiu7 chai Seng3-keng si7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7, hiah e5 sian-ti siu7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kam2-tong7 lai5 sia2--e5.
Goa2 ti7 pek-chhiat ki5-to2 tiong tin3-cheng7 goa2 e5 sim, toan7-choat8 kap goa7-kai3 kau-thong e5 si5, chiu7 jip8 ti7 kap Seng3 Sin5 e5 kau-thong, thiaN-kiN3 Seng3 Sin5 sou2 kong2 e5, che chiu7-si7 u7-gian5 e5 Sin5, Siong7-te3 tui3 goa2 kong2 koan-he7 kau3-hoe7, chu7-hoe7, ko3-jin5, kok-ka, goa2 pun2-sin, ki5-thaN cheng2-cheng2 e5 su7 e5 pi3-bit8, ia7 u7 kong2 kau3 koan-he7 Bi2, Sou e5 kun-pi7, ti7 chia be7 thang kong-piau2, goa2 bo5 chhut-khi3 soan2-ku2, chong2-si7 goa2 kiu5 Siong7-te3 tui3 thiN lai5 chiang2-li2 kok-cheng3, koan-he7 chhu3-kau3 e5 siu2-siong3 sim2-mih8 lang5 beh tong3-soan2 ia7 u7 tit-tioh8 khe2-si7. Chit e5 su7 ti7 chu7-hoe7 kian3-cheng3, hou7 in chai hit e5 chin-sit8. Chong2-si7 goa2 sou2 tit-tioh8 u7-gian5 e5 un-su3 iau2 si7 chhou-ki5, boe7 thang sng3 choe3 sim2-mih8, na7 tit jip8 koh khah chhim Sin5 e5 chhim-hai2 e5 si5, chiu7 oe7 kiah8 pit lai5 sia2, na7 si7 su7-sit8 tak8-jit8 u7 tit-tioh8 thiN e5 khe2-si7, i2-kip8 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kau-thong, hiah siong5-se3 seng5-liok8.
“Tioh8 kiu5 jin5-ai3, iah8 tioh8 chhiat-chhiat him-bou7 siok8 Sin5 e5 un-su3; khah iau3-kin2 e5 si7 choe3 sian-ti lai5 thoan5-to7.” (I Ko-lim5-to 14:1) Chong2-si7 leng5-tek e5 su7, u7 thang kiaN e5 gui5-hiam2, chiu7-si7 Seng3 Sin5 teh choe3 kang, mou5-kui2 ia7 teh siong3 ki-hoe7, phaiN2-sin5 li7-iong7 lang5 e5 jiok8-the2 e5 loan2-jiok8 lai5 khi-phian3 lang5. Koh ka-ki7 liah8 choe3 siu7 Seng3 Sin5 chhiong-moa2, siu7 chiok-hok e5 lang5, put-ti put-kak, siu7 in2-iu2 jip8 Mou5-kui2 e5 sia5-lou7, in-ui7 an2-ni Seng3 Leng5 chu2-gi7 e5 lang5 choe7-choe7 poah8-to2. Goa2 ti7 khi2-chhou e5 kui2-ni5 kan, tui3 in e5 kiat-ko2 lai5 hun-piat8 si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 lai5 a2-si7 tui3 phaiN2-sin5 lai5, chiu7 chai, ng3 ka-ki7 oan5-choan5 sun7-than3 Chu2, ti7 Seng3 Sin5 kau-thong e5 si5, sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 chiah si7 chin-sit8, ia7 chai na7 chhin-chhiuN7 sio2-eng2 e5 chha2-nau7, kam2-kak phah loan7 cheng7-siok8 e5 si5, si7 phaiN2-sin5 chhun-chhut iu2-hek8 e5 chhiu2 e5 si5, hit si5 sou2 siu7 tioh8--e5 siong5-siong5 si7 ke2--e5. Tui3 an2-ni it-hoat kiaN-ui3 Siong7-te3, chun-tiong7 seng3-kiat, hoan2-seng2 kau3 it-gian5 it-gu2 e5 jit8-siong5 seng-oah8.
Tui3 se3-jin5 kian3-cheng3 tui3 Siong7-te3 sou2 seng5-siu7--e5, si7 loa7-nih8 chin-sit8, lai5 siu7 te7 saN-chia2 kong-peng5 e5 phoe-phoaN3, chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, goa2 sou2 hoat-piau2 leng5-tek su7-kiaN7, a2-si7 koan-he7 chiong-lai5 e5 u7-gian5 si7 khak-sit8. Ti7 Chu2 bat goa2 e5 hiaN-che2 ia7 po2-cheng3 chiah e5 su7 si7 chin-sit8. Siong7-te3 seng3-kiat e5 cheng7-siok8 tiong teh kong2, ia7 tioh8 chai phaiN2-sin5 si7 ti7 chha2-nau7 tiong teh kong2. Na7 ui7-tioh8 leng5-tek beng5-u7-sim, a2-si7 ui7-tioh8 li7-ki2-sim lai5 li7-iong7 ti7 hia chiu7 siN-chhut sia5-kau3, chiu7 Ki-tok e5 sin3-tou5 ia7 siu7 khi-phian3. Tioh8 keng2-seng2 tioh8 ki5-to2, goa2 tak8-jit8 siu7 Chu2 in2-chhoa7 u7 kui2 na7 tiam2-cheng ki5-to2 e5 si5-kan, u7 si5 10 goa7 tiam2 cheng chiong sim chip8-tiong choan ng3 Siong7-te3, m7 si7 tak8-lang5 long2 oe7 chit khoan2 e5 seng-oah8, lang5 e5 bin7-heng5 bo5 sio-siang7, un-su3 a2-si7 hong7-su7 ia7 koh-iuN7. Tok8-tok8 chit8-hang7; chiu7-si7 khun5-thak8 Seng3-keng chiap-siu7 choe3 seng-oah8 e5 kng, ti3-i3 kap Siong7-te3 saN-kap kiaN5 e5 seng-oah8, ban7-lang5 long2 chit8-iuN7. Ti7 chit chan5 khak sin3 Siong7-te3 chiong I e5 oe7 siuN2-su3 jin5-lui7, khi3-sak leng5-tek ia2-sim, piaN3-khang ka-ki7, lai5 tui-chhe7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7; si7 an-choan5 kap peng5-ho5 e5 po2-cheng3, che si7 thau3 kau3 thiN i5-it oah8-mia7 e5 sio2-lou7. A-men.
“In-ui7 Ia5-sou e5 kan-cheng3 chiu7-si7 sian-ti e5 sin5.” (Khe2-si7-liok8 19:10) Ti7 chia kian3-cheng3 koan-he7 u7-gian5 e5 su7-sit8, lai5 eng5-iau7 Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 Sin5. 7 ni5-cheng5 goa2 siu7 chhiaN2 kau3 HoaiN5-pin, ti7 Giam5-kan-ke (岩間町) u7 2 e5 kho2-keng3 Sui7-tian2 (Sweden) e5 soan-kau3-su ti7 hia choe3 soan-kau3-su e5 kang, goa2 siu7 chhiaN2 si7 beh eng3-oan7 thian-bou7 pou3-to7, tu2-chiah tah ho2, iau2-be7 khai-si2 pou3-to7, na7 si7 u7 chin toa7 e5 chhi3-tham3, hoat-chhut hong-thai keng2-po3, u7-ko3 u7 lek8-su2 siong7 khong-chian5 e5 hong-thai beh thong-ke3 Koan-tong . Moa2 ke kiaN-hiaN5, thiN-khi3 chiam7 ok-hoa3 hong-sok na2 toa7, chiau3 tian7-tai5 e5 po3-sang3 HoaiN5-pin e5 sio2 hak8-hau7 i2-keng theng5-kho3, ke-nih tiam3-thau5 ia7 long2 koaiN-tiam3, hong-sok na2 kiong5 e5 tiong-kan tui3 kok ka-teng5 chhut khin-khong kio3 e5 siaN, theh8 chhut choan5 lat8 teh keng2-kai3 chun2-pi7. 2 e5 soan-kau3-su ti7 chit khoan2 kiaN-hiaN5 e5 tiong-kan lai5 chhe7 goa2, chham-siong5 beh siu thian-bou7, goa2 in3 kong2 “chiam7 chhiaN2 theng3-hau7, goa2 ki5-to2 Siong7-te3 chiah ka7 lin2 hoe5-hok8”, chiu7 giong2-bong7 Siong7-te3.
Soan-kau3-su put-bin5 put-hiu teh kou3-siu2 thian-bou7, chiau3 thiaN he si7 chioh e5, na7 phah-phoa3 tioh8 poe5, sit8-chai7 si7 chin sui2 e5 toa7 thian-bou7. Goa2 chiong sim piaN3 chhut ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 ki5-to2 “kiu5 ka3-si7 goa2 chai Li2 e5 chi2-i3.” Chit si5 thiN khui, tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 khe2-si7. Ti7 iN7-siong7-tiong khoaN3-kiN3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 chhu2 jin5-keh tui3 Siong7-te3 hia hong7-chhe lai5 goa2 chia, hit e5 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 “Lin2 tioh8 tiaN7-tiaN7, tioh8 chai Goa2 si7 Siong7-te3; Goa2 beh ti7 liat8-pang tiong choe3 koaiN5 toa7, siu7 chun choe3 toa7.” (Si-phian 16:10) 2 e5 soan-kau3-su hoan5-lo2 hoan5-lo2 koh lai5 chhe7 goa2 “Cho2-tin5 hiaN-ti7 taN chaiN2-iuN7?” Goa2 in3 kong2 “Siong7-te3 teh po2-siu2, thian-bou7 m7 thang siu.” Hit si5 hong-sok 15 kong-chhioh toa7 chhiu7 toa7 io5-tang7. Goa2 ia7 thong3-kam2 chek-jim7 bo5 li7-khui Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5, oan5-choan5 sin3-kho3 Chu2, hian3 kam2-sia7 e5 ki5-to2.
Chiau3 po3-sang3 hong-thai khai-si2 choan2 hong-hiong3, choan5-leng5 e5 Siong7-te3, chu5-pi e5 ThiN-pe7, ka7 hit e5 toa7 hong-thai koa3 phi7-khoan5, beng7-leng7 i choan2 hong-hiong3; “che si7 lou7, li2 tui3 chia khi3” Ha-le-lu-iah u7-gian5 u7 si5 ti7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 toa7 kng tiong, thiaN Siong7-te3 sou2 kong2, u7 si5 ti7 iN7-siong7 tiong khoaN3-kiN3, koh u7 si5, ti7 seng3 e5 lim5-chai7 tiong chiaN5-choe3 bo5 siaN e5 oe7, u7 si5 siu7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 bek8-si7. Chong2-si7 long2 si7 tui3 sam-ui7 it-the2 e5 Siong7-te3 sou2 su3, hit e5 pun2-goan5 chi2 u7 si7 Chu2. Ti7 Pak-liok8 e5 toe7 ia7 u7 sio-siang7 e5 keng-giam7, u7 thoan5-to7-chia2 kong2 “Bi7 cheng-iu2 e5 beng2 hong-thai ta3-moa2 Pak-liok8, thian-bou7 kaN2 tioh8 siu khi2-lai5!” ThiaN-kiN3 an2-ni li2 soan-kau3-su lai5 ka7 goa2 kong2, goa2 in3 kong2 “Goa2 beh ki5-to2, chhiaN2 theng3-hau7”, chiu7 the3-jip8 bak8-pang5, siau-hong5-chhia thang kiaN e5 keng2-tek8 tui3 chhi7 lai5 thoan5-po3, chiam7-chiam7 khai-si2 thau3 toa7 hong, goa2 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 tin3-cheng7 sim-sin5, chi2-u7 thai7-bong7 I e5 seng3-chi2 e5 si5, ang5 sin3-ho7 tu5-khi3, Chu2 kong2 “m7 bian2 siu thian-bou7”, kau3 e5-hng chiong chit e5 su7 ka7 soan-kau3-su kong2, chong2-si7 sio2-sim e5 Jit8-pun2 lang5 thoan5-to7-chia2 i2-keng siu khi2-lai5 lah, chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni Siong7-te3 eng7 u7-gian5 e5 sin5 lai5 kong2, chong2-si7 ui7-tioh8 beh hou7 goa2 pun2-sin bo5 ham7-loh8 chu7-ko; hou7 lin2 chai u7 siu7 loa7 giam5-tiong7 e5 koan2-li2.
Cha2-jit8 tui3 ka-ki7 e5 jiat8-sim koh ke-thiN seng3 e5 ia2-bong7 e5 he2, chiaN5-choe3 jiok8-the2 e5 un7-heng5, m7-chai hou7 Seng3 Sin5 loa7-nih8 iu-bun7 le3. ThiN-pe7 chhim-chai chit chan5 su7, chiu7 eng7 piN kap chhe5 giam5-giam5 keng2-kai3 goa2 chhin-chhiuN7 chek-tok su-seng chu2, u7 si5 tang7-tang7 heng5-hoat8 goa2, chu7-ko hoan7-choe7 ti3-kau loh8 te7-gek8, put-ju5 bo5 eng7 Sin5 e5 un-su3 hou7 i khah ho2, khiam-sun3 kin2-sin7 thiaN3 Siong7-te3, keng3-tiong7 chhu3-piN, khoaN3 pat8 lang5 khah iaN5 pun2-sin e5 sin3-giong2 seng-oah8, si7 choe3 te7-it si3-chiaN3 e5 lou7. A-men.
